        Lovosis Technology LLC, Dubai, is the authorized distributor of UNV Smart Interactive Panels
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl dark:text-gray-200">
      <p class="animate-slide-in-left delay-100">
